With the spark plug temp sensor at #3 I have noticed different temp
readings depending on the outside temp and where my cooling flaps were
as the thermostat was operating adding or restricting air to the
cylinders.

67 Single Cab, DP 1641cc 34 PICT-3 (Thumper)
71 Trike 1776cc Dual T-4 34 PDSIT-3
VolksAir 1585cc 31 PICT
